ked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T21:52:07.000Z","msg":"當全世界都開始封鎖中國，香港已經沒有活路<br />\n<br />\n中共政權的最高指導原則是維護政權，不是照顧人民。所以最好的防護設備，都分發給公安和解放軍。<br />\n相同的道理，港共為了維護政權，當然囤積防護設備給警察。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KPZ23jBpgwU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKPZ23jBpgwU&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ3vcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=f3b309a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KPZ23jBpgwU</a><br />\n<br />\n海峡论谈：美中军机台海角力 美议员提台湾SOS法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0NGRZXZPY7w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0NGRZXZPY7w&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ3vcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=291b0612\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0NGRZXZPY7w</a><br />\n<br />\n習近平政權不穩，中共國即將爆炸<br />\n香港獨立，唯一出路"},{"pid":"0cb55ba30a942960a9863e9ac5dda7371583731c","tid":1883252,"uid":38861,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T22:15:04.000Z","msg":"睇完成篇文，完全搵唔到邊一句有講病毒係人工合成。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，有唔少冠狀病毒都有文中所指的Furin cleavage site，引起老鼠肝炎的MHV（Mouse hepatitis virus)就係其中一個例子。<br />\n<br />\n如果病毒擁有Furin cleavage site的話，亦即是代表病毒有機制可以避開lysosomal inhibitor的截擊。<br />\n<br />\n現今中國有幾項Clinical Trial都嘗試緊用Chloroquine（主治瘧疾的lysosomal inhibitor)醫治肺炎病人，而依篇文章有證據顯示Chloroquine有好大機會唔會有醫治成效。"},{"pid":"ec4b2a65b84fcc4422ccf30499033d2e90040930","tid":1883252,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T22:22:39.000Z","msg":"好快被消失"},{"pid":"0a3d1411206860a3dfa26a2b5a76f39f0dfab3f8","tid":1883252,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0cb55ba30a942960a9863e9ac5dda7371583731c","tid":1883252,"uid":38861,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T22:15:04.000Z","msg":"睇完成篇文，完全搵唔到邊一句有講病毒係人工合成。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，有唔少冠狀病毒都有文中所指的Furin cleavage site，引起老鼠肝炎的MHV（Mouse hepatitis virus)就係其中一個例子。<br />\n<br />\n如果病毒擁有Furin cleavage site的話，亦即是代表病毒有機制可以避開lysosomal inhibitor的截擊。<br />\n<br />\n現今中國有幾項Clinical Trial都嘗試緊用Chloroquine（主治瘧疾的lysosomal inhibitor)醫治肺炎病人，而依篇文章有證據顯示Chloroquine有好大機會唔會有醫治成效。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T00:03:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打讀biochem?"},{"pid":"6b5a7ff17eedbef53c6f2ca8122180030e0c033f","tid":1883252,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95843a52fa339cf097909ba64fe36a524c3abe4f","tid":1883252,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T21:45:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://sohfrance.org/wufeiyannandawenzaoyixinguanbingdurengonghecheng/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsohfrance.org%2Fwufeiyannandawenzaoyixinguanbingdurengonghecheng%2F&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ3vcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=a326fc46\" target=\"_blank\">https://sohfrance.org/wufeiyannandawenzaoyixinguanbingdurengonghecheng/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://sohfrance.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/%E6%8D%95%E8%8E%B722-scaled.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsohfrance.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F%25E6%258D%2595%25E8%258E%25B722-scaled.jpg&h=8f80d1db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【2020年2月15日】（歐洲希望之聲何梓涵綜合報導）今日，有網友發現，南開大學生命科學學院、南開大學數學院聯手其他高校於1月27日共同發表的《武漢2019冠狀病毒S蛋白可能存在Furin蛋白酶切位點》論文中，早已證實引發武漢肺炎疫情的新型冠狀病毒為人工合成。<br />\n<br />\n網友稱這是中共內部團隊發表的論文，論文默認了病毒是人工合成的。也有網友稱，之前的懷疑都是真的，這病毒是集sars、艾滋、埃博拉特性於一身的高傳染的末日武器！<br />\n<br />\n論文於1月27日發表在中國科學院科技論文預發布平台上，最後修改日期是2月2日。目前仍可從該網站上下載到此論文。<br />\n<br />\n文中論述到：比對武漢2019新型冠狀病毒與SARS之間交界區核酸序列，發現變異來源是插入了12個鹼基，這種改變將更多地使病毒通過直接膜融合的方式感染細胞，故具有更高的侵染性。<br />\n<br />\n隨著時間的推移，武漢肺炎疫情正在演變為一場全球性的危機。<br />\n<br />\n日本今（15）日再次刷新單日確診記錄，新增12例病例，全境累計53例，其中死亡1例。據日本《共同社》報導，今日新增案例中，有8人為東京的出租車司機，其中7人都接觸過早前被確診的1名司機；另有3名出現在和歌山縣湯淺町濟生會有田醫院，該院早前1名醫生和1名患者被確診，目前該院被懷疑可能出現院內傳染。<br />\n<br />\n鑽石公主號再傳驚人感染數字，今日確診67例，全船累計285例。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，歐洲首現死亡案例，死者是早前在法國被確診的1名80歲的中國遊客。<br />\n<br />\n泰國新增1例，患者為35歲的女性醫務人員，目前累計34例。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡新增5例，都有與已確診病例接觸的記錄，新加坡是中國之外確診數量最高的國家，累計72例。<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞新增2例達21例，患者皆為中國公民。<br />\n<br />\n非洲首現武漢肺炎確診病例。埃及在周五（14日）證實，1名男性非埃及公民被確診感染武漢肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n世衛組織官員一直憂心，大量的中國人在非洲生活工作，而非洲國家的衛生系統，幾乎無法應對這種公共衛生緊急事件，醫界擔心埃及病例會引爆另一波疫情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://sohfrance.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/1-5-scaled.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsohfrance.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F1-5-scaled.jpg&h=118db163&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://sohfrance.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/2-4-scaled.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsohfrance.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F2-4-scaled.jpg&h=fbec310f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://sohfrance.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/3-4-scaled.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsohfrance.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F3-4-scaled.jpg&h=7c4afa4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://sohfrance.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/4-scaled.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsohfrance.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F4-scaled.jpg&h=c4ee38f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://sohfrance.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/5-7-scaled.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsohfrance.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F5-7-scaled.jpg&h=ca03273d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://sohfrance.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/6-scaled.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsohfrance.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F6-scaled.jpg&h=6c688964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無高手分析下呢篇野可唔可信?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked